00:03:49.111 --> 00:03:53.780
if u are following me on other medias like 
 Instagram, you might already know but 

00:03:55.051 --> 00:03:57.340
i had my hair dyed.

00:03:58.173 --> 00:04:07.900
i dont think you can see the actual color under this 
 shitty lighting but i got some gold and red streaks.

00:04:09.948 --> 00:04:17.630
